<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Han er her! Halleluja!
 Han er her! Amen!
 Han er her! Ære, Ære!
 Jeg vil prise Hans navn.
 Han er her, lytt nøye,
 Hør Han kaller på ditt navn.
 Du vil aldri bli den samme,
 Han er her, Gud er sann!

[V2]
 He is here, hallelujah
 He is here, amen
 He is here, holy, holy
 I will bless His name again
 He is here, listen closely
 hear Him calling out your name
 He is here, you can touch Him
 You will never be the same</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<title>Han er her! Halleluja!</title>
<presentation>v1 v2 </presentation>
</song>